You can simply ask Alexa to control your “ibesom A3 Plus robot vacuum ”. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our “ibesom” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in “ibesom” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable “ibesom” skill, and you'll be navigated to “ibesom” login page;
(4) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the ibesom robot.”
“Alexa, turn off the ibesom robot.”
